id: "class:cleric#crashing_wave"
name: "Crashing Wave"
description: "Clerics revere their deity as the embodiment of nature and the incarnation\
  \ of wind and waves. Clerics who live in or near the sea sometimes embrace the watery\
  \ aspect of their deity's other dimensions and take the title of crashing wave.\
  \ In aquatic communities, a crashing wave is often a healer and spiritual leader.\
  \ Such clerics understand the tempestuousness and cruelty of the sea, but also its\
  \ generosity and bounty."
modifications:
